name: Worldwide Knives Discount Knife Emporium
overview: Worldwide Knives, Inc. sell all kinds of knives that you can imagine from the common kitchen knife to striking replicas of swords from popular fantasy movies. We have knives for specific uses as well as handy utility and pocket knives that serve a number of purposes. Quality is never a problem as our knives are manufactured by some of the most trusted brands in the industry. Paul Clarence is an ardent knife collector. He started his knife collection when he got his first job right after he finished college. What started as a hobby became a passion, and now he owns WorldwideKnives.com. Paul is a sports and fitness enthusiast. He plays basketball, football, tennis, and works out at the gym regularly. He rides a Ducati motorcycle and is into rock and alternative music.
